I have alot of /'s cause my equipment changes depending on the situation.
Forexample when fighting warriors (non casters) I wear my AC rings as magic
resist doesnt hurt. When Pulling in HATE, I wear my TBB (cause I wont be
fighting anyway and would need the AC). etc etc.
